<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="AtlasPay is a PayPal-class global payouts platform concept focused on speed, trust, compliance, and simple user experiences.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="global payouts app, business payouts, freelancer payments, secure wallet, double-entry ledger, KYC, AML, payment compliance">
    <title>AtlasPay - Global Payouts Built for Speed and Trust</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            color-scheme: light;
            --bg: #f5f8ff;
            --bg-soft: #eaf1ff;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --ink: #102033;
            --muted: #5f6f83;
            --primary: #1157ff;
            --primary-dark: #0734a8;
            --accent: #00b894;
            --warning: #ffb020;
            --border: #d9e2f2;
            --shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(16, 32, 51, 0.12);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--ink);
            background: var(--bg);
            font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
        }

        .skip-link {
            position: absolute;
            left: -999px;
            top: 16px;
            z-index: 10;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: var(--primary-dark);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .skip-link:focus {
            left: 16px;
        }

        header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 5;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
        }

        .nav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 24px;
            width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 16px 0;
        }

        .brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .brand-mark {
            display: grid;
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            border-radius: 12px;
            place-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(17, 87, 255, 0.25);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 22px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-links a:focus,
        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 46px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: var(--primary);
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 999px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(17, 87, 255, 0.24);
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .button:hover,
        .button:focus {
            background: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .button.secondary {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        main {
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        section {
            width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 0.9fr);
            gap: 44px;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 720px;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            width: fit-content;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            background: #e9efff;
            border: 1px solid #cbd8ff;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }

        h1,
        h2,
        h3 {
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.06;
            letter-spacing: -0.045em;
        }

        h1 {
            max-width: 760px;
            margin-top: 18px;
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.4rem);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 4.4rem);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
        }

        .lead {
            max-width: 690px;
            margin: 22px 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: clamp(1.08rem, 2vw, 1.28rem);
        }

        .hero-actions,
        .cta-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .proof-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 34px;
        }

        .proof {
            padding: 18px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 22px;
        }

        .proof strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1.65rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        }

        .proof span {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .phone-shell {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 420px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 18px;
            background: #071121;
            border-radius: 42px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .phone {
            overflow: hidden;
            min-height: 620px;
            padding: 22px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f6f9ff 100%);
            border-radius: 30px;
        }

        .phone-top,
        .phone-row,
        .receipt-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .avatar-group {
            display: flex;
        }

        .avatar {
            display: grid;
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            margin-left: -8px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: var(--primary);
            border: 3px solid #ffffff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            place-items: center;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .avatar:first-child {
            margin-left: 0;
            background: var(--accent);
        }

        .balance-card {
            margin-top: 28px;
            padding: 22px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #102a68, #1157ff);
            border-radius: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 22px 48px rgba(17, 87, 255, 0.28);
        }

        .balance-card small,
        .receipt small,
        .status-pill {
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .balance-card strong {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            line-height: 1;
            letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        }

        .send-panel,
        .receipt,
        .mini-card {
            padding: 18px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(16, 32, 51, 0.08);
        }

        .send-panel {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .steps {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 14px 0 0;
        }

        .step {
            padding: 10px;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            background: var(--bg-soft);
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 0.84rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .receipt {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .status-pill {
            padding: 6px 10px;
            color: #08624f;
            background: #dffbf2;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
        }

        .section-head {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(280px, 0.65fr);
            gap: 28px;
            align-items: end;
            margin-bottom: 34px;
        }

        .section-head p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .card {
            padding: 26px;
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(16, 32, 51, 0.07);
        }

        .card p {
            margin: 12px 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .icon {
            display: grid;
            width: 46px;
            height: 46px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            border-radius: 16px;
            place-items: center;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .feature-list,
        .check-list {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 18px 0 0;
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .feature-list li,
        .check-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 28px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .feature-list li::before,
        .check-list li::before {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--accent);
            content: "\2713";
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .flow {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .flow-step {
            position: relative;
            padding: 24px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 28px;
        }

        .flow-step strong {
            display: inline-grid;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            place-items: center;
        }

        .split {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(320px, 1.1fr);
            gap: 28px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .panel {
            padding: 34px;
            background: #071121;
            border-radius: 34px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .panel p,
        .panel li {
            color: #c2d0e2;
        }

        .ledger {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 22px;
        }

        .ledger-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .calculator {
            display: grid;
            gap: 14px;
            padding: 26px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        label {
            display: grid;
            gap: 8px;
            color: var(--ink);
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        input,
        select,
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 13px 14px;
            color: var(--ink);
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #cbd6e8;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font: inherit;
        }

        input:focus,
        select:focus,
        textarea:focus,
        button:focus,
        a:focus {
            outline: 3px solid rgba(17, 87, 255, 0.22);
            outline-offset: 3px;
        }

        .summary-box {
            display: grid;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 18px;
            background: var(--bg-soft);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .summary-box div {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .cta {
            width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin-bottom: 80px;
            padding: 54px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 0%, rgba(0, 184, 148, 0.38), transparent 32%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #071121, #102a68);
            border-radius: 38px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .cta p {
            max-width: 720px;
            color: #d6e1f0;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 36px 16px;
            color: #c2d0e2;
            background: #071121;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        @media (max-width: 960px) {
            .nav {
                align-items: flex-start;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }

            .hero,
            .section-head,
            .split {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .hero {
                min-height: auto;
                padding-top: 54px;
            }

            .grid,
            .flow {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            section {
                padding: 56px 0;
            }

            .nav-links {
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .proof-row,
            .grid,
            .flow,
            .steps {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .phone {
                min-height: auto;
            }

            .cta {
                padding: 32px 22px;
            }
        }

        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            *,
            *::before,
            *::after {
                scroll-behavior: auto !important;
                transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to main content</a>
    <header>
        <nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
            <a class="brand" href="#home" aria-label="AtlasPay home">
                <span class="brand-mark">A</span>
                <span>AtlasPay</span>
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#users">Users</a></li>
                <li><a href="#platform">Platform</a></li>
                <li><a href="#controls">Controls</a></li>
                <li><a href="#compliance">Compliance</a></li>
                <li><a href="#demo">Fees</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a class="button secondary" href="#contact">Request pilot</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main id="main">
        <section id="home" class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
            <div>
                <span class="eyebrow">PayPal-class payout operations</span>
                <h1 id="hero-title">Move money globally with speed users feel and controls finance teams trust.</h1>
                <p class="lead">AtlasPay is a product blueprint for consumer, freelancer, and business payouts where every send flow is simple, every fee is visible, and every critical payment action is protected by ledger-grade safeguards.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a class="button" href="#demo">Estimate a payout</a>
                    <a class="button secondary" href="#controls">Review safeguards</a>
                </div>
                <div class="proof-row" aria-label="Key product promises">
                    <div class="proof"><strong>3 taps</strong><span>send money flow</span></div>
                    <div class="proof"><strong>24/7</strong><span>status visibility</span></div>
                    <div class="proof"><strong>AA</strong><span>accessibility baseline</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="phone-shell" aria-label="Mobile payout app preview">
                <div class="phone">
                    <div class="phone-top">
                        <strong>Wallet</strong>
                        <span class="status-pill">Protected</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="balance-card">
                        <small>Available balance</small>
                        <strong>$18,420.00</strong>
                        <div class="phone-row">
                            <span>USD wallet</span>
                            <span>MFA on</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="send-panel">
                        <div class="phone-row">
                            <strong>Send to Maria</strong>
                            <div class="avatar-group" aria-hidden="true">
                                <span class="avatar">M</span>
                                <span class="avatar">B</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="steps" aria-label="Three-tap payout flow">
                            <span class="step">1. Choose</span>
                            <span class="step">2. Review</span>
                            <span class="step">3. Send</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="receipt">
                        <div class="receipt-row">
                            <small>Before you confirm</small>
                            <span class="status-pill">No surprises</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="summary-box">
                            <div><span>Recipient gets</span><strong>$495.12</strong></div>
                            <div><span>Fee</span><strong>$4.88</strong></div>
                            <div><span>ETA</span><strong>Today</strong></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mini-card" style="margin-top: 16px;">
                        <strong>Next step</strong>
                        <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted);">Receipt, tracking link, support path, and dispute options are ready immediately.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="users" aria-labelledby="users-title">
            <div class="section-head">
                <div>
                    <span class="eyebrow">Product outcomes</span>
                    <h2 id="users-title">Simple enough for first-time users. Powerful enough for global teams.</h2>
                </div>
                <p>Each workflow exposes trust cues at the point of decision: identity status, exact fees, ETA, receipt, cancellation window, and support path.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid">
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">C</span>
                    <h3>Consumers</h3>
                    <p>Sign up, complete KYC, link funding sources, send, receive, request, refund, and dispute money in plain language.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">F</span>
                    <h3>Freelancers</h3>
                    <p>Receive cross-border payouts, export transaction history, track tax-friendly receipts, and keep clients informed.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">B</span>
                    <h3>Businesses</h3>
                    <p>Run single and batch payouts with approvals, limits, status tracking, exports, and operational reconciliation.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="platform" aria-labelledby="platform-title">
            <div class="section-head">
                <div>
                    <span class="eyebrow">Non-negotiable capabilities</span>
                    <h2 id="platform-title">Every money movement feature has a product surface and a control surface.</h2>
                </div>
                <p>The app is designed as vertical slices: auth, wallet, transfer, ledger, reconciliation, risk, and support.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid">
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">1</span>
                    <h3>Secure access</h3>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>MFA, device trust, and session controls.</li>
                        <li>Step-up verification for risky actions.</li>
                        <li>Accessible onboarding and KYC guidance.</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">2</span>
                    <h3>Wallet and funding</h3>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>Stored value wallets where licensed.</li>
                        <li>Tokenized bank and card connections.</li>
                        <li>Pre-confirmation fee and ETA preview.</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">3</span>
                    <h3>Payout operations</h3>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>Single, request, receive, and batch payout flows.</li>
                        <li>Live status, notifications, and exports.</li>
                        <li>Refunds, disputes, receipts, and support trails.</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="flow-title">
            <div class="section-head">
                <div>
                    <span class="eyebrow">3 taps to send</span>
                    <h2 id="flow-title">The happy path is short. The guardrails are always on.</h2>
                </div>
                <p>Progressive disclosure keeps the core flow calm while advanced controls remain available for limits, purpose codes, funding source changes, and recipient details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flow">
                <article class="flow-step">
                    <strong>1</strong>
                    <h3>Choose recipient</h3>
                    <p>Saved contacts, verified businesses, and clear identity confidence signals.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="flow-step">
                    <strong>2</strong>
                    <h3>Enter amount</h3>
                    <p>Limits, currency, delivery speed, and funding options are checked instantly.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="flow-step">
                    <strong>3</strong>
                    <h3>Review terms</h3>
                    <p>Fees, FX, ETA, protection, and cancellation rules appear before confirmation.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="flow-step">
                    <strong>4</strong>
                    <h3>Track payout</h3>
                    <p>Receipt, payment status, support, refund, and dispute actions stay attached.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="controls" class="split" aria-labelledby="controls-title">
            <div>
                <span class="eyebrow">Financial integrity</span>
                <h2 id="controls-title">Ledger-first architecture for money movement that cannot guess.</h2>
                <p class="lead">Critical payment intents use idempotency keys, double-entry ledger events, immutable audit trails, and reconciliation from internal ledger to processor and bank settlement.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Exactly-once semantics for payment intent transitions.</li>
                    <li>Fraud scoring, velocity limits, configurable rules, and manual review.</li>
                    <li>KYC, KYB, sanctions screening, AML monitoring, and regional policy gates.</li>
                    <li>Traces, metrics, logs, anomaly alerts, backups, runbooks, and rollback plans.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="panel" aria-label="Ledger event example">
                <span class="eyebrow" style="color: #b7ffe9; background: rgba(0,184,148,0.14); border-color: rgba(0,184,148,0.36);">Double-entry example</span>
                <div class="ledger">
                    <div class="ledger-row"><span>Debit user wallet</span><strong>-$500.00</strong></div>
                    <div class="ledger-row"><span>Credit payout clearing</span><strong>+$500.00</strong></div>
                    <div class="ledger-row"><span>Debit payout clearing</span><strong>-$495.12</strong></div>
                    <div class="ledger-row"><span>Credit recipient settlement</span><strong>+$495.12</strong></div>
                    <div class="ledger-row"><span>Credit fee revenue</span><strong>+$4.88</strong></div>
                </div>
                <p>Ledger entries are append-only and reconcile against processor status and bank settlement files.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="compliance" aria-labelledby="compliance-title">
            <div class="section-head">
                <div>
                    <span class="eyebrow">Compliance by design</span>
                    <h2 id="compliance-title">Trust is visible in the interface and enforceable in the platform.</h2>
                </div>
                <p>Legal, privacy, and licensing constraints are treated as product requirements, not cleanup work after launch.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid">
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">P</span>
                    <h3>PCI scope minimization</h3>
                    <p>Tokenize card data through PSPs wherever possible and keep sensitive payment data out of core app systems.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <span class="icon">S</span>
                    <h3>SOC 2 control posture</h3>
